title: Vox for 90, Birk for 90!
description: PA starts the show with Boudreau! Plus plenty of sports talkers including previewing the NFL Combine! Speaking of the Combine, Nordo and PA check out at the half way point to catch their flight to Indy, and Matt Birk guides the love covenant the rest of the show! Please join us!
